{"tid":570996,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國擬改憲法宣誓詞 加入「強國」","createTime":"2018-02-24T09:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T10:41:45.000Z","uid":35790,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"93caddd1f2bb3cf1ae7ca24b326236298100108b","tid":570996,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T09:05:07.000Z","msg":"中國擬改憲法宣誓詞 加入「強國」<br />\n<br />\n23日召開的12屆全國人大常委會第33次會議，擬對憲法宣誓制度相關規定作出適當修改，明確監察委員會組成人員依法產生後應當進行憲法宣誓、宣誓儀式應當奏唱中華人民共和國國歌。憲法宣誓誓詞將從70字修改為75字，其中有關奮鬥目標的表述也將修改為「為建設富強民主文明和諧美麗的社會主義現代化強國努力奮鬥！」<br />\n<br />\n大公報報導，中國憲法宣誓制度在2015年中確立，於2016年1月1日開始正式實施。官方媒體稱，此次憲法宣誓制度的修改，旨在貫徹落實19大和19屆二中全會精神，適應深化國家監察體制改革的需要，完善憲法宣誓制度，進一步弘揚憲法精神、彰顯憲法權威。<br />\n&lt;聯合&gt;"},{"pid":"4067d6b25fe7971a110de0afb3c4b2824289c9f0","tid":570996,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T09:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b0e0a20b83303317a4bbbabe738cad6a305ced","tid":570996,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T09:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/24/171346_a1a53d6410fee1af5db3aef5476ac93d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F24%2F171346_a1a53d6410fee1af5db3aef5476ac93d.gif&h=f72a3e1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0402cfb2b35cbddf73360b7e8fa9a1542791e38e","tid":570996,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T09:14:33.000Z","msg":"弘揚小強精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c0a9ed4f58c01e2f888d2823601c550679b156","tid":570996,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T09:18:17.000Z","msg":"美國宣誓有冇 strong nation / strong state / strong country ?"},{"pid":"d849adf70649524b53543ae074f7b2e9cb222fbc","tid":570996,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s